{"lemma":"ضامِنَةٍ","slug":"ضامِنَةٍ","root":"ض.م.ن","root_slug":"ض-م-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ض-م-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n26050"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B6%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%90%D9%86%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26050","headword_ar":"ضَامِنَةٌ","root":"Dmn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[fem. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAminN","text_ar":"ضَامِنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlD~aAminapu","text_ar":"الضَّامِنَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is included within the middle"},{"kind":"text","text":"of any town or country or the like. (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlD~aAminapu mina Aln~axoli","text_ar":"الضَّامِنَةُ مِنَ النَّخْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AO, S, K, * TA,) occurring in a letter of the Prophet, (AO, S, TA,) means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What are included within the cities"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"towns"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"villages, of the palmtrees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AO, S, K, * TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what are surrounded, thereof, by the wall of the city:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) but Az says that they are so called because their owners are responsible for their culture and keeping: (TA:) opposed to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlD~aAHiyapu mn Alb~aEoli","text_ar":"الضَّاحِيَةُ من البَّعْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which means what are in the open country, of the palm-trees that imbibe with their roots, without being watered. (AO, S, TA. *)"}],"source_refs":["AO","S","TA","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}